<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Sep 2024 00:41:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列司法部长预计推迟任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</link><description>一位与司法部长亚里夫·莱文关系密切的人士表示，“他不会做一个好孩子，安静地接受裁决”，他指的是最高法院要求他必须任命一位新总统的裁决，“但他也不会违反这一裁决”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:41:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-justice-minister-expected-to-delay-appointment-of-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d331-dd1c-a19b-d33157550000</guid></item><item><title>他们为赫什·戈德堡-波林和奥里·达尼诺而战。在湿婆节，他们见到了家人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</link><description>达尼诺和戈德伯格-波林一家上周在相距几英里的地方举行了湿婆礼，但认识并不是人们来到他们家的先决条件。一位曾拜访过这两家公司的人士表示，“我是来安慰自己的，也希望得到一点安慰”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 20:04:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/they-fought-for-hersh-goldberg-polin-and-ori-danino-at-the-shiva-they-met-the-families/00000191-d30d-d83f-a3d9-df5fa95c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡自己的话暴露了他的失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡的说法——哈马斯独自阻止了一项协议——证明了他的策略的失败，如果一开始就有策略的话</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 19:48:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-08/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-own-words-reveal-his-failure/00000191-d308-d9f1-add1-f7be7fff0000</guid></item><item><title>“这是我的职责”：是什么让这些活动分子来到约旦河谷的一个巴勒斯坦小镇</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</link><description>自10月7日以来，以色列定居者以约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦城镇的al-Auja溪流为目标，切断当地人的水源。一群以色列人和巴勒斯坦人在现场游行，决心因剥夺和战争而“圣化生命”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 18:35:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/palestinians/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/its-my-duty-what-brings-these-activists-to-a-palestinian-town-in-the-jordan-valley/00000191-c236-db84-a3bd-eb7e5b650000</guid></item><item><title>摩尔多瓦拒绝批准降落后，乌曼飞往哈西德派犹太人的航班可能会被取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</link><description>成千上万想要参观布拉茨拉夫拉比·纳赫曼坟墓的持票人已被告知，摩尔多瓦政府拒绝批准布拉茨拉夫·哈西丁飞经基希讷乌机场。正在探索飞往罗马尼亚的替代航班</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:15:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/uman-flights-for-hasidic-jews-may-be-canceled-after-moldova-refuses-to-approve-landings/00000191-d25a-deaf-a1f1-dfff71d30000</guid></item><item><title>目击者称以色列军队在没有发生冲突的情况下射杀了美国活动家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</link><description>“我们站着，军队可以看到，只是站在那里什么也不做。什么也没发生。我听到两声枪响，”一位也参加了艾森努尔·埃兹吉·埃吉被杀的示威活动的抗议者说道</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:13:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/eyewitness-says-israeli-army-shot-american-activist-when-there-were-no-clashes/00000191-d202-df60-a79b-d27f4be50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第338天：外国外交官称停战谈判“没有任何进展”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</link><description>约旦人向以色列-约旦边境口岸开火，造成三名以色列人死亡 ■ 熟悉停战谈判的消息人士：“只有当双方都认为有兴趣时才会发生” ■ 以色列安全内阁周日晚间讨论协议 ■ 以色列国防军：向北部发射了 50 枚火箭弹以色列从黎巴嫩出发 ■ 欧盟外交政策负责人启程参加停火运动，并在埃及和黎巴嫩停留，但不包括以色列 ■ 战争结束 338 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 17:02:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-338-truce-talks-not-progressing-anywhere-foreign-diplomat-says/00000191-d289-d214-a393-d7b956770000</guid></item><item><title>Nur Shams 和 Tul Karm 被毁的街道不容置疑。约旦河西岸是战区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-destroyed-streets-in-tul-karm-leave-no-room-for-doubt-the-west-bank-is-a-war-zone/00000191-cd0e-df60-a79b-cd7fe8730000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦居民说，“这是企图将我们连根拔起，他们试图将难民营的居民从我们的家中连根拔起，但我们不会去。”随着以色列军队加强在西岸北部难民营的行动，居民担心该地区将成为新的加沙</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:23:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-destroyed-streets-in-tul-karm-leave-no-room-for-doubt-the-west-bank-is-a-war-zone/00000191-cd0e-df60-a79b-cd7fe8730000</guid></item><item><title>“对以色列存在明显的偏见”：10 月 7 日 BBC 加沙战争报道报道</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/report-accuses-bbc-of-anti-israel-bias-during-war-in-gaza/00000191-d1cb-d214-a393-d5fb39460000</link><description>《每日电讯报》的报道称，“调查结果揭示了 BBC 存在令人深感担忧的偏见模式，并且多次违反其有关公正、公平和确立真相的编辑指南”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 15:10:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/report-accuses-bbc-of-anti-israel-bias-during-war-in-gaza/00000191-d1cb-d214-a393-d5fb39460000</guid></item><item><title>呼吁达成人质协议的被拘留抗议者表示，他们被问及是否得到报酬</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/detained-protesters-calling-for-hostage-deal-say-they-were-asked-if-theyre-being-paid/00000191-d1cb-d25e-a1f7-d7cb85260000</link><description>三名被捕的抗议者表示，他们被带到以色列中部的一名情报官员那里，该官员试图获取有关抗议组织者的信息。一名被拘留者说，“他询问资金问题，甚至提到了埃胡德·巴拉克”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:50:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/detained-protesters-calling-for-hostage-deal-say-they-were-asked-if-theyre-being-paid/00000191-d1cb-d25e-a1f7-d7cb85260000</guid></item><item><title>以色列海岸发现极度濒危吉他鱼的天然苗圃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</link><description>小黑鳅吉它鱼栖息在马甘迈克尔的砂岩海湾中，直到达到足以勇敢面对公海的临界尺寸</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:34:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/nursery-for-critically-endangered-guitarfish-identified-off-israeli-coast/00000191-d12e-dd1c-a19b-d13f67a60000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争成为威尼斯电影节的焦点，获奖者声援巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦和美国犹太导演都因其电影获奖，直接解决了这一冲突。斯坎达尔·科普蒂说：“我们的电影着眼于道德叙事如何将我们团结在一起......但同时也让我们对他人的痛苦视而不见。”</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 14:13:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/leisure/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-takes-spotlight-at-venice-film-festival-as-winners-voice-support-for-palestinians/00000191-d11e-df60-a79b-d17fbffd0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院命令司法部长任命新最高法院院长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-orders-justice-minister-to-appoint-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d17e-df60-a79b-d17fd8ed0000</link><description>这项裁决是对以色列质量政府运动提交的请愿书的回应，该请愿书声称司法部长亚里夫·莱文未能推进任命程序并非善意且涉及别有用心</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 12:15:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-orders-justice-minister-to-appoint-new-supreme-court-president/00000191-d17e-df60-a79b-d17fd8ed0000</guid></item><item><title>约旦枪手在过境点枪击事件中杀死三名以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/jordan-citizen-kills-three-israeli-security-guards-in-shooting-attack-at-allenby-crossing/00000191-d0dd-deaf-a1f1-ddff0b330000</link><description>约旦当局正在调查事件的细节。以色列和约旦之间的所有过境点将关闭，直至另行通知</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 10:42:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/jordan-citizen-kills-three-israeli-security-guards-in-shooting-attack-at-allenby-crossing/00000191-d0dd-deaf-a1f1-ddff0b330000</guid></item><item><title>2500 年前，Halfat 陶工得到了一座房子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-09-08/ty-article/halfat-the-potter-gets-a-house-2-500-years-ago/00000191-d0f1-d25e-a1f7-d7fb8ff60000</link><description>考古学家推断出一项交易的细节，其中包含一个不寻常的警告，用古阿拉姆语写在古代以色列某处的迦南罐子上</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 10:13:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2024-09-08/ty-article/halfat-the-potter-gets-a-house-2-500-years-ago/00000191-d0f1-d25e-a1f7-d7fb8ff60000</guid></item><item><title>在平民闯入以色列军事基地后，本格维尔的秘书告诉警察不要使用武力</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-secretary-told-cops-not-to-use-force-after-civilians-broke-into-idf-base/00000191-cde5-d214-a393-cdfdcd150000</link><description>7月，在军警因涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯而逮捕以色列国防军士兵后，以色列人袭击了两个军事基地，其中包括拘留士兵的拜特利德基地。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔下令对骚乱者从轻处理</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:08:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvirs-secretary-told-cops-not-to-use-force-after-civilians-broke-into-idf-base/00000191-cde5-d214-a393-cdfdcd150000</guid></item><item><title>尽管遭到质疑，美国还是敲定了新的以色列与哈马斯停火提案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-finalizing-new-israel-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-despite-skepticism/00000191-ce14-dd1c-a19b-cf35a77b0000</link><description>美国的努力主要集中在三点，其中以色列从加沙撤军是一个特别严峻的挑战</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:03:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/u-s-finalizing-new-israel-hamas-cease-fire-proposal-despite-skepticism/00000191-ce14-dd1c-a19b-cf35a77b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府的世界末日愿景：将加沙变成约旦河西岸，将约旦河西岸变成加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</link><description>忘掉在本格维尔的诽谤吧：以色列正面临真正陷入泥潭的风险，因为它着眼于对加沙的军事统治，而约旦河西岸的局势正在各个层面升级</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 03:02:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/israels-new-task-the-gazafication-of-the-west-bank/00000191-ce12-d214-a393-cfba5b7c0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，未经他允许，部长们不会访问圣殿山/阿克萨大院</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</link><description>以色列国防军：夜间从黎巴嫩向以色列发射了约 50 枚火箭弹；无人员伤亡 ■ 约旦表示正在调查与以色列边境发生的致命枪击事件，关闭过境点直至另行通知 ■ 加沙消息来源报道，加沙北部救援部门副指挥官在贾巴利亚家中遇袭身亡</description><pubDate>Sun, 08 Sep 2024 01:54:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article-live/reports-three-rescuers-killed-in-israeli-attack-in-lebanon-drone-sirens-in-north-israel/00000191-cf4f-d25e-a1f7-cfcff8cb0000</guid></item><item><title>法院命令释放涉嫌向本格维尔扔沙子的女子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</link><description>特拉维夫治安法院法官在观看该事件的短视频后中断听证会，随后将嫌疑人软禁，整个法庭都在抗议对她的拘留。</description><pubDate>Sat, 07 Sep 2024 21:50:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-08/ty-article/.premium/woman-suspected-of-throwing-sand-at-ben-gvir-released-by-court-order/00000191-ce49-d25e-a1f7-cfcb46e60000</guid></item></channel></rss>